name: YoOoNGZ #4
description:
☆ ☆ They are not what you think they are.


The guy was waiting for me inside his car. As the uber was pulling off, I saw he had a dog inside the car with him. But it was not any kind of dog. Scary-ass-trong-as-hell kind of dog, you know?

We met in front of the gym, shook hands, did a little small talking and went up to the office. I was there to grab the footage of the earlier shooting we had at the guy’s gym. I really wanted to see the images.

The guy went up the stairs right behind me. We entered the office, he put away his backpack in the chair, let go of the dog’s chain and

Smoothly dropped his gun on the table.

I Transfered the images to my SSD already calling an Uber and was out of there in 3 minutes.
